sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant SM as SubmissionModal
    participant S as Supabase
    participant A as Admin
    participant N as Notification

    Note over U,N: === 사용자 맛집 제보 흐름 ===
    
    U->>F: Click "맛집 제보" Button
    F->>F: Check Auth Status
    alt Not Logged In
        F->>U: Show AuthModal
        U->>F: Login
    end
    
    F->>SM: Open RestaurantSubmissionModal
    U->>SM: Fill Form
    Note right of SM: restaurant_name<br/>address<br/>youtube_link<br/>category<br/>description
    
    SM->>SM: Validate Form
    SM->>S: Insert to restaurant_submissions
    Note right of S: status = 'pending'
    S->>SM: Return Success
    SM->>U: Show Success Toast

    Note over U,N: === 관리자 심사 흐름 ===
    
    A->>S: Query pending submissions
    S->>A: Return submissions list
    A->>A: Review submission
    A->>S: Geocode address (Naver API)
    S->>A: Return coordinates
    
    alt Approve
        A->>S: Insert to restaurants
        A->>S: Update submission status = 'approved'
        S->>N: Trigger notification
        N->>U: New restaurant notification
    else Reject
        A->>S: Update submission
        Note right of S: status = 'rejected'<br/>rejection_reason = '...'
    end

    Note over U,N: === 사용자 제보 현황 확인 ===
    
    U->>F: Open MyPagePanel
    F->>S: Query user's submissions
    S->>F: Return submissions
    F->>U: Show submission status
    Note right of U: pending: 심사중<br/>approved: 승인됨<br/>rejected: 거절됨 + 사유
